Set Hostname on Ubuntu Server 16.04 LTS
/etc/hosts

127.0.0.1       localhost
127.0.1.1       backsync        ubuntu
                    ^
                    |
                    |
                    |
                    |
               Set Your Hostname
               
# The following lines are desirable for IPv6 capable hosts
::1     localhost ip6-localhost ip6-loopback
ff02::1 ip6-allnodes
ff02::2 ip6-allrouters

/etc/hostname
backsync
